===Etymology===
First attested in the late 14th century. From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|acusacion|lang=fro}} (French {{term|accusation|lang=fr}}), from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|accusatio|accūsātiō|accusation, indictment|lang=la}}, from {{term|accuso|accūsō|blame, accuse|lang=la}}. More at {{term|accuse|lang=en}}.

